.TH UMKOIN "1" "January 2026" "umkoin v30.1.0rc1" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
umkoin \- manual page for umkoin v30.1.0rc1
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B umkoin
[\fI\,OPTIONS\/\fR] \fI\,COMMAND\/\fR...
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-m\fR, \fB\-\-multiprocess\fR
Run multiprocess binaries umkoin\-node, umkoin\-gui.
.TP
\fB\-M\fR, \fB\-\-monolithic\fR
Run monolithic binaries umkoind, umkoin\-qt. (Default behavior)
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Show version information
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Show full help message
.SS "Commands:"
.TP
gui [ARGS]
Start GUI, equivalent to running 'umkoin\-qt [ARGS]' or 'umkoin\-gui [ARGS]'.
.TP
node [ARGS]
Start node, equivalent to running 'umkoind [ARGS]' or 'umkoin\-node [ARGS]'.
.TP
rpc [ARGS]
Call RPC method, equivalent to running 'umkoin\-cli \fB\-named\fR [ARGS]'.
.TP
wallet [ARGS]
Call wallet command, equivalent to running 'umkoin\-wallet [ARGS]'.
.TP
tx [ARGS]
Manipulate hex\-encoded transactions, equivalent to running 'umkoin\-tx [ARGS]'.
.TP
help
Show full help message.
.SS "Additional less commonly used commands:"
.TP
bench [ARGS]
Run bench command, equivalent to running 'bench_umkoin [ARGS]'.
.IP
chainstate [ARGS] Run umkoin kernel chainstate util, equivalent to running 'umkoin\-chainstate [ARGS]'.
test [ARGS]       Run unit tests, equivalent to running 'test_umkoin [ARGS]'.
test\-gui [ARGS]   Run GUI unit tests, equivalent to running 'test_umkoin\-qt [ARGS]'.
